  Last night on at lerast 6 different mobs, i stole agro from the MT when the mob was below 70%.  Not using Slow.  Not using DoT, the only nukes i used was frost and spear when they were up.  Those 2 spells and melee and I kept getting agro.  They try to claim it was unlucky ripostes.  Kinda hard to make that claim when you see the message: "You will not evade me Vecsus" followed by "XXX Rampages on Vecsus".   Now I have decent HPs (about 7300 raid buffed) but my little leather-clad ass is not designed to take a rampage from a mob that quads for 1200.   BST melee is not so excessive that we should be stealing agro from 4-5 different warriors and assorted other melee.<br />_________________<br />Vecsus Strangiato &lt;Enlightened Dark&gt;
