			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">The taunt button by itself is inadequate anyway. First the taunt has to succeed. Second, a successful taunt will move the warrior to the top of the hate list , but only just barely. If a warrior is already at the top of the hate list then repetetive mashing of the taunt button is useless as the hate gained from taunt isn't cumulative. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
This is one thing alot of people dont understand.  Unless the warrior has some good taunt weapons (stunning blow etc), it is hard to hold aggro with just taunt.  As Ragash said, the taunt button only momentarily puts the war at the top of the hate list.  If someone gains aggro between the time the warrior hits taunt and the time the taunt button refreshes, the warrior really cant do anything.  
<br />

<br />
And also like Ragash said, its not cumulative.  Its kinda like a guy running a race that gets a burst of speed every couple of seconds.  He stays ahead of the rest of the pack, but only barely, and only due to his short bursts of speed.  Sometimes other runners will pass him up, but only untill he gets his next burst of speed.  Sometimes the other runners get too far ahead and his bursts of speed do nothing.  Thats when the rezzes begin hehe.
<br />

<br />
But in your case Vecsus, id have to ask what other melees were on the mob?  If it was you and a bunch of warriors and only one was taunting, i can see you outdamaging them and getting some aggro.  But if you had some bards/rogues/monks/or rangers in there, they should have got aggro way before you.  
<br />

<br />
Okay just scrolled up and saw you said you had other assorted melee in there too.  Hmm.  Maybe you just more uba than ya thought  <img src="images/smiles/icon_twisted.gif" alt="Twisted Evil" border="0" />  hehe<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=584848" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=584848</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
