				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If the MT is actually trying to keep agro and you succeed and getting it from him then it is your fault.
<br />

<br />
It takes two to tango. If they are trying to do their job and you take agro from them there is nothing they can do.
<br />

<br />
If you can get agro by just swinging away then you should stop swinging for a second or two. It might take a little longer time to kill the mob but CR will take longer still. Sometimes killing the mob fast isn't the most efficient way.
<br />

<br />
